#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"Selection determines which elements will be the target of our actions. "
"Selections work on the current scene visible objects. Blender has "
"advanced selection methods. Both in *Object Mode* and in *Edit Mode*."
msgstr ""
"选择决定哪些元素将成为我们操作的目标。选择在当前场景中工作的可见物体。"
"Blender有先进的选择方法。都在 *物体模式* 和 *编辑模式* 。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:14
msgid "Selections and the Active Object"
msgstr "选择和激活对象"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:16
msgid "Blender distinguishes between two different states of selection:"
msgstr "Blender 区分两种不同状态的选择："

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:20
msgid ""
"Unselected object in black, selected object in orange, and active object "
"in yellow."
msgstr "未选中的对象为黑色，选定的对象为橙色，激活的对象为黄色。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:23
msgid ""
"In *Object Mode* the last (de)selected item is called the \"Active Object"
"\" and is outlined in yellow (the others are orange). There is exactly "
"one active object at any time (even when nothing is selected)."
msgstr ""
"在 *物体模式* 中，最后一个选定的项目被称为“激活物体”，并用黄色（其他为橙"
"色）轮廓外框表示。任何时候都有且只有一个激活物体（即使没有选择任何东"
"西）。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:27
msgid ""
"Many actions in Blender use the active object as a reference (for "
"example linking operations). If you already have a selection and need to "
"make a different object the active one, simply re-select it with :kbd:"
"`Shift-RMB`."
msgstr ""
"Blender中的许多命令都使用激活物体作为参考（例如链接操作）。如果你已经有选"
"择一个物体，并且需要选择了一个不同的激活物体，只需使用 :kbd:`Shift-RMB` "
"重新选择它。"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/selecting/introduction.rst:31
msgid ""
"All other selected objects are just selected. You can select any number "
"of objects. In order to change a property or to perform an operation on "
"all selected objects (bones, and sequencer-strips) hold :kbd:`Alt`, "
"while confirming."
msgstr ""
"所有其它选定的物体只是被选中。你可以选择任意数量的物体。为了改变属性或对"
"所有选定的物体（骨骼和音序列条）执行操作，请按住  :kbd:`Alt`，同时确认。"
